---
title: Mexican Chicken & Garlic Rice with Cherry Tomato Salsa & Mini Corn Cobs
description: One of the best part of Mexican for dinner is getting to pick and choose between all the yummy bits! This bowl has garlic-infused rice plus spiced tender chicken pieces, a fresh and bright cherry tomato salsa and mini corn cobs. The hardest part of the meal is choosing what bite to eat first!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5c19fb8ce3f3393c4e098622-76eaf789.jpg
